Reticulum transport and propagation node plugin for OPNsense. Provides
full GUI configuration of the Reticulum cryptographic networking stack
including all interface types (LoRa/RNode, TCP, UDP, Serial, KISS,
AX.25, I2P, Auto), transport node routing, and LXMF propagation node
store-and-forward messaging. Includes service management, automatic
firewall rule generation, and network diagnostics.

WWW: https://reticulum.network/
